headline: 5 Revealing Analyst Questions From CVS Health’s Q3 Earnings Call
summary: CVS Health’s third quarter was shaped by strong top-line momentum across its core businesses, notably pharmacy and health insurance, with management attributing results to improved execution in retail pharmacy, market share gains, and early progress on Aetna’s operational turnaround.
